uk.gov.gchq.palisade.policy.tuple

Class PalisadeTuple

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.gov.gchq.palisade.policy.tuple.PalisadeTuple
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<Object>, uk.gov.gchq.koryphe.tuple.Tuple<String>

    public class PalisadeTuple
extends Object
implements uk.gov.gchq.koryphe.tuple.Tuple<String>
    A PalisadeTuple is a Tuple that wraps a record, User and Context in a record and allows users to select fields based on field names. The field names have namespaces, such as: User.auths, User.userId.id, Context.context, Record.timestamp
